[[["nummod", "dep", "det", "nmod", "case"], "Unit 2  A Lesson in Forgiveness."], [["advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "cop", "det", "nsubj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "dep", "det"], "When I was a kid, I delivered newspapers in my community every day."], [["nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "compound", "nsubjpass", "nmod:poss", "cc", "conj", "auxpass", "dep", "parataxis", "nsubj", "advmod", "dobj", "det", "amod", "compound", "advcl", "mark", "cop", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "acl", "mark", "dobj"], "On a quiet Saturday afternoon, my friend and I were bored, so we randomly picked an old ladys house to be part of our game of throwing stones."], [["nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "ccomp", "nsubj", "det", "nmod", "case", "advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "det", "compound", "cc", "conj", "compound:prt", "nmod", "case", "det"], "We wanted to see the stones turn into missiles as they rolled to the roofs edge and shot out into the yard."], [["nmod", "case", "nsubj", "advmod", "nmod", "case", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "det"], "To me, they looked just like comets that fell from the sky."], [["nsubj", "dobj", "det", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det"], "I found a stone and sent it for a ride."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "det", "cop", "advmod", "xcomp", "mark", "dep", "parataxis", "nsubj", "compound:prt", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "dobj"], "However, the stone was too smooth to grasp, so it slipped out of my hand when I threw it."], [["nsubj", "dobj", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "det"], "It hit a small window in the ladys house with a crash."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubjpass", "auxpass", "advcl", "mark", "auxpass", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "det", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod"], "Since we were frightened of being caught, we escaped at the sound of the broken glass."], [["nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "amod", "nsubjpass", "auxpass", "advmod", "nmod", "case", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "aux", "neg", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "cc", "conj", "nmod:poss", "amod"], "For the next few days, I was so worried about myself that I did not think of the old lady and her broken window."], [["advmod", "advmod", "advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "cop", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "xcomp"], "Later on, when I was sure that I wasnt in trouble, I started to feel guilty."], [["nmod:tmod", "det", "nsubj", "det", "amod", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "xcomp", "nsubj", "det", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "xcomp", "xcomp", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "advmod"], "Every day, the old lady greeted me with a warm smile as I passed her the paper, but I didnt feel comfortable in her presence anymore."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "compound:prt", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "acl", "mark", "dobj", "det", "acl:relcl", "dobj", "nsubj", "advcl", "mark", "dobj"], "Finally, I made up my mind to save the money which I made from delivering newspapers."], [["nsubj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "nummod", "aux", "dobj", "det", "acl", "mark", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "cc", "conj", "nmod", "case", "nummod", "nsubj", "xcomp", "nsubj", "det", "nummod"], "I calculated that seven dollars should cover the cost of repairing her window, and in three weeks, I had the seven dollars ready."], [["ccomp", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case", "det", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "det", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "nsubj", "cop", "advcl", "mark", "dobj", "nmod:poss"], "I put the money in an envelope and wrote a note that said, I am sorry for breaking your window."], [["nsubj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "det", "aux", "dobj", "det", "acl", "mark", "dobj"], "I hope that the money will cover the cost of repairing it."], [["advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "cop", "nsubj", "advmod", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "compound", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss"], "When it was dark, I crept quietly to the old ladys house and slipped the envelope under her door."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "advmod", "nsubj", "dobj", "amod", "cc", "conj", "advcl", "mark", "dobj", "nmod", "advmod", "case", "det", "advmod", "advmod"], "After I did so, I felt relieved and couldnt wait to look her straight in the eye once again."], [["nmod:tmod", "det", "amod", "nsubj", "iobj", "det", "amod", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "cc", "conj", "advmod", "dobj", "det", "amod", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "nmod", "case"], "The next day, I handed the old lady her paper and happily returned the warm smile that I received from her."], [["nsubj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "cc", "conj", "iobj", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case"], "She thanked me for the paper and gave me a bag of cookies."], [["nsubj", "dobj", "cc", "conj", "advmod"], "I thanked her and then left."], [["nsubj", "compound:prt", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "det"], "I walked away and enjoyed the cookies."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case", "det", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "compound:prt"], "After I had eaten several, I discovered an envelope inside the bag and pulled it out."], [["advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "dobj", "compound:prt", "nsubj", "cop", "advmod"], "When I opened it up, I was very surprised."], [["nmod", "case", "det", "expl", "nsubj", "det", "nummod", "cc", "conj", "det", "amod", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "appos", "compound", "nmod", "case"], "In the envelope, there were the seven dollars and a short note that said, Im proud of you!"], [["nmod", "case", "compound"], "XAdapted from True Forgiveness."]]